      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected with literature justification. Power-law hemolysis model exponents taken from Giersiepen et al. without sensitivity analysis to alternative parameterizations. Model form uncertainty not propagated to QoI. Achieved level 2; required level 4 not met."
