    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD model provides sufficient evidence to support hemolysis predictions for the VAD COU. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed and results fall within acceptable bounds at the design operating point. Partial gaps in several credibility factors are acknowledged; the team judges residual uncertainty to be manageable given conservative safety margins applied to the clinical threshold. Assurance level declared Medium reflecting the partial evidence base.",
